summary: 检测易宝OA系统中ExecuteQueryNoneResult和ExecuteQueryForDataSetBinary接口是否存在SQL注入漏洞，通过发送特定payload并测量响应延迟来判断漏洞是否存在
summary_en: Detect SQL injection vulnerabilities in the ExecuteQueryNoneResult and ExecuteQueryForDataSetBinary interfaces of YiBao OA system. It determines the existence of vulnerabilities by sending specific payloads and measuring response delays.
